N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7859.1 - General

State Regulations

This Part sets forth information filing requirements, as
determined by the board or by the chair as authorized by the board, applicable
to major petroleum suppliers and any other entity that the board deems
appropriate to collect such information. Notes
